將發射首發星，搭載的相關載荷具有在軌可重構技術，能夠開展通信體制驗證，實現小型終端聯試聯調、星地業務試運行，並對衛星測控運管系統進行驗證。<br />\n<br />\n星座建成後，智能手機將直接進入衛星應用領域，支持用戶從地面網絡切換到衛星網絡，用戶終端不變、體驗不變，同時可提供兩極地區空間組網覆蓋、全球通信服務保障、天基導航授時服務、航空航海監視和支持智能終端的互聯網及物聯服務，實現&ldquo;用溝通連接萬物、讓全球永不失聯&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n導讀：<br />\n<br />\n鴻雁星座計劃目的，並非真正提供全覆蓋通訊，而是要與Space X搶軌道+頻譜，以免Space X的Starlink會突破中國的防火牆城<br />\n<br />\n貿易戰未打嚮，科技戰太空戰已開波<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:31:28.000Z","msg":"太空垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一陣搞到成天都係阿古哲斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:36:24.000Z","msg":"支那哩個擺到明係鎖國用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a8f25d31477ef5772a18cf0bf2fdb3c449e58b","tid":575675,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c84d4955cb4697ae1f7cf6957eb56c1aa58f6199","tid":575675,"uid":43770,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:35:28.000Z","msg":"中學都教過衛星不嬲係上網最慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:47:55.000Z","msg":"重睇內文啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9004509acaeaa7ebb407910cf896acb52040754","tid":575675,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c84d4955cb4697ae1f7cf6957eb56c1aa58f6199","tid":575675,"uid":43770,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:35:28.000Z","msg":"中學都教過衛星不嬲係上網最慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:55:04.000Z","msg":"日新月異"},{"pid":"183a0d4c05f966a78ad7f5706cb8d4818a43699d","tid":575675,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass