 LeoSat<br />\n- BlackSky"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T15:52:26.000Z","msg":"睇完呢堆野<br />\nGoogle呢啲先係科技公司<br />\n700？呢種無實力公司已經去到不斷spin off 先暫時頂得住個expected growth<br />\n你買埋我嗰份"},{"pid":"cb451b3b467f0cd05c2434f773bfbfe61a032596","tid":575675,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T15:57:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完呢堆野<br />\nGoogle呢啲先係科技公司<br />\n700？呢種無實力公司已經去到不斷spin off 先暫時頂得住個expected growth<br />\n你買埋我嗰份</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nGoogle 嘅 X Projects 應該係真正背後策劃者<br />\n當年用汽球嘅諗法隨住space X可以降成本之後<br />\n就開始真正落實，X Projects賺唔賺錢真係唔知<br />\n但每樣計劃背後都係想改變世界格局"},{"pid":"644788ebf332f1acd54eebe728fb77c7f8e6ad7e","tid":575675,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee2187bbda51bc511a9c421a1ba7364d84abaa75","tid":575675,"uid":19557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"438a811b7aa84a15f780db1fd2aa74192723edba","tid":575675,"uid":5253,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b4a3811c6ca6007dbb28b7ba1e9a4573d3633432","tid":575675,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:43:10.000Z","msg":"無處不在 但無處不慢咁有撚用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:49:12.000Z","msg":"唔係個個地方有得上網喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至少行船個班有用先"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T15:32:55.000Z","msg":"如果行船可以上網 我諗會多左好多人行船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T16:12:53.000Z","msg":"行船最大問題就係呢樣嘢"}]}